Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:21.70,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天悄悄许下的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:26.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直被封闭着静止不动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.86,0:00:32.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犹如梦境般的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:38.13,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,描画了出色的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:44.12,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在未来等待  想象那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.12,0:00:47.14,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加无法入眠 并非没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.37,0:00:52.15,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此次相遇发生奇迹般的改变
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.41,0:00:53.17,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:54.63,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.78,0:00:56.15,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.15,0:00:58.77,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出色的队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.97,0:01:01.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在星空飞扬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.41,0:01:04.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高歌源于勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.88,0:01:06.24,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.31,0:01:07.79,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:10.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深不可测的价值观
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.73,0:01:16.23,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伟大的人物从不孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.54,0:01:25.99,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路标一定直指前方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.72,0:22:42.21,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜空の赤と長く伸びた影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.21,0:22:46.38,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつの間にか　二番星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.92,0:22:50.78,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰のためそして何のために
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.78,0:22:55.03,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この限りない世界はある
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:23:04.61,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それは　あ～　答えを聞くためではなく　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.92,0:23:13.00,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ただ　ここにいる一人の人が繋がれば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.22,0:23:17.22,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全な世界　みんな会いで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.40,0:23:23.12,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てしない世界　自分を知る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.12,0:23:27.48,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放て　希望の矢を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.87,0:23:31.14,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ただ　叶いとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:35.62,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全な世界　みんな会いで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:41.26,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てしない世界　自分を知る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.44,0:23:45.83,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放せ　闇の影を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.96,0:23:50.03,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まだ　見えなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.72,0:22:42.21,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤色夜空 长长延伸的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.21,0:22:46.38,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知什么时候出现了第二颗星星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.92,0:22:50.78,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了谁 又是为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.78,0:22:55.03,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了这无边无际的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:23:04.61,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是　啊 不是为了寻求答案
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.92,0:23:13.00,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 如果能和这里的一个人相连
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.22,0:23:17.22,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在完美世界 我们相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.40,0:23:23.12,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在没有尽头的世界 我们了解了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.12,0:23:27.48,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放出希望之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.87,0:23:31.14,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 即便能够实现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:35.62,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在完美世界 我们相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:41.26,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在没有尽头的世界 我们了解了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.44,0:23:45.83,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,释放黑暗的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.96,0:23:50.03,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是还没看见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.03,0:23:52.03,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.51,0:01:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆一行在旅途中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一个叫杰达·拉科斯帕的圣职者相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.36,0:01:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰达性情善良 而且还是个大力士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而巴隆一行对他的行动却一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.92,0:02:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便这样还是和他一起与占领村子的僵尸战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临别时巴隆一行和他约定再会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.63,0:02:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随后向着新的城镇出发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:19.48,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(349,238)}暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:19.48,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(376,392)}鬼神的眼睛也会流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说 就是这个路程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你这样的小姑娘在 真是被治愈了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 有在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 离城镇还远吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.12,0:02:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说达库里斯镇是最近的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在你们还是别去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个城镇不安定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有传言说有鬼神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.21,0:02:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫罗克希的鬼神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗克希是那个鬼剑士的罗克希吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.68,0:02:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对鬼剑士罗克希有兴趣吗 年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:03:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉德大陆中传说中的女剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过听说已经死了很长时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的还真是详细啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为老夫对可爱的通吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老夫我可是什么都知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.33,0:03:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据传 罗克希是巨乳而且喜欢男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时拥有不计其数男人的了不得的黑毒药
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.86,0:03:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 那家伙还真是了不得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的 谎言 谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能相信这个老头儿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷爷 要走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 要去达库里斯镇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这点小事没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 不用介意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.29,0:04:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快点去抓那个冒牌货
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪是我啊 一点都不像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是鬼剑士罗克希只有你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是背黑锅啊 给我做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是快乐的旅行 年轻人们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.12,0:05:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就此分别吧 我会想你们的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去铲除鬼神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁太阳还没落山 必须去采购了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也该换一件新衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我点钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.17,0:05:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情 就别找我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.47,0:05:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.05,0:05:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 应该还有点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点事 分开行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 即使挖地三尺也要把那家伙找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的倒容易
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 到底藏在什么地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是赶得上还好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在鬼神流泪之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了 罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 应该说是冒牌的罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.22,0:06:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一样 也是被厌恶的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么又要假冒罗克希之名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我继承了鬼剑士罗克希之名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.11,0:07:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑士罗克希是心灵的支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想变成罗克希那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么要不要加入我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够给你罗克希之名哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身体已经
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 所以才来邀请你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.86,0:07:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们见识一下你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:07:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就是条件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打败一个嚣张的鬼剑士 对你来说很简单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢 听说闹得挺厉害的 不过没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想和杀人的鬼神扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非 你也是鬼剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全找不到线索啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的还在这个镇上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.55,0:08:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了 冒牌罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用这把罗克希之剑杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗克希应该已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.29,0:08:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是罗克沙诺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我是一个村子的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得这么强硬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才这种程度 看来还没有鬼神化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.22,0:09:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经鬼神化了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经只能以鬼神的身份活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能够回头的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.84,0:09:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很害怕 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太天真了 看招
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:09:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好用你的眼睛看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在死之前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼神化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南来北往的客官
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走过路过不要错过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的表演很精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未完待续的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEY BABY
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在我的怀中撒娇 哭泣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太接近我的话 心也会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有鬼神出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又出现鬼神了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼神 莫非是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方已经无药可救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.33,0:11:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请你做罗克希的对手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:11:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你吗 罗克沙诺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要妨碍我们 老头儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开 年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不让你吃点苦头你是不会明白的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这老头儿怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.51,0:12:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是那个老爷子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡鲁 你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们快去救那个小子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让他也变成鬼神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.46,0:12:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.72,0:12:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不快去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的对手是老夫 年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.23,0:13:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道老夫的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点 巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.67,0:13:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这点本事吗 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说有人盯上了鬼剑士 是你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:13:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来 巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不到我说的了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙了啊 那家伙已经不是人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不救他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止我们不是被巴隆救过好多次了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.75,0:14:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次轮到我们来救他了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没那么容易
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 我救 我救就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只有一次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务艰巨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不让他安定下来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.28,0:15:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快冻住他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.48,0:15:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒悲鸣洞穴那里的那家伙之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切就都全部结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在这之前 我的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.07,0:15:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是你在救我 这次换我来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿甘多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让这些孩子留下那样的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借给我力量吧 阿甘多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人流泪就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的份 巴隆的份都由我来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流泪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是伊鲁贝克大人的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要杀罗克沙诺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:17:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡鲁松
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也像她一样没有去处被人类厌恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收留这样的我的不就是你吗伊鲁贝克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.83,0:18:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗克沙诺流泪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就此了结她对她来说或许更加幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不再出现那样的鬼神我们所应走的路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令我在意的还有另外一个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人的力量不可小觑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.11,0:19:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吵啊 再让我多睡一会嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.11,0:19:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是在担心我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会为你担心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这次真是累死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷爷 你的胳膊没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心老夫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羁束器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的可以收下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是老夫的朋友特制的羁束器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.02,0:20:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给需要的人是最合适不过的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗克沙诺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了 变得很精神了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.86,0:20:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然从那个状态回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是靠自己的力量回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.38,0:20:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许有人代替你流泪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.79,0:20:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:21:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到下个城镇之前我的行李就归你负责没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.52,0:21:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃这么多的点心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这次没买新衣服以后慢慢的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你说什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说一遍 再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.24,0:21:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也没说 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个羁束器已经交给他了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.17,0:21:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受阿甘多所托好不容易把羁束器带给了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个羁束器应该给还有未来的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.31,0:22:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果老夫早点找到你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.58,0:22:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的命就
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.17,0:22:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 从变身为鬼神的那一刻起这种事早就注定了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.36,0:22:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定我现在很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.88,0:22:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在我生命的最后见到了巴隆和罗克希
